 
## 3 STEPS FOR BUILDING Text CLASSIFICATION


1) Build docker:

    1.1)Open terminal and go to current working directory
    
    1.2)RUN : docker build -t Text_classification .
    
    

2) TRAINING

 2.1)RUN : cd  Classification_model/        (if you are not in this directory)

 2.2)RUN : docker run -i --rm -v `pwd`:/home:rw Text_classification:latest python3 train.py


Note: Input data is in input folder and the format must me same as input.csv



3) INFERENCE

3.1) RUN: docker run -it -p 8888:8888 third:latest

3.2) RUN: jupyter notebook --ip=0.0.0.0 --port 8888 --no-browser --allow-root

3.3) RUN: inference.ipynb


  
